Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:20.55,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと前から決まっていたような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:26.12,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠い昔からわかってたような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:32.06,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない線の上をたどるように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:37.84,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導かれ出逢い 交差するSaison
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:43.76,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背中合わせの光と影のように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:49.45,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強く引かれる　Mystification
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:55.20,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳元で囁き呼ぶ声に振り向けば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:01.05,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かぬうち開かれていたトビラ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:06.81,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少しの偶然と必然をつなぐように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:12.22,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動き始めた二つのHistoire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:24.73,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと果てなく続いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:20.55,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很久以前就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:26.12,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很久之前就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:32.06,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛行走在看不见的线上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:37.84,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被牵引的邂逅 交错的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:43.76,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一纸相隔的光与影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:49.45,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被强烈吸引的Mystification
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:55.20,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在耳边轻轻细语 转头一看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:01.05,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不经意间已经打开的门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:06.81,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小小的偶然与必然有着不可分割的联系一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:12.22,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与开始变化的两段历史一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:24.73,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远 无尽地持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了引出我母親柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才被移送至此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我嚎叫著求救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽就一定會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人…布洛瓦侯爵是如此認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是與他的意思相反 我卻一直保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算我嚎叫了 媽媽也不一定會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？但她是妳母親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道了妳正在受罪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我真的很小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經見過媽媽一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這個 我無論何時都會來救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管身處何方 我都會趕來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個吊墜換句話說就是我們母女間羈絆的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻把那個證明…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 維多利加她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 你已經像這樣來迎接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像平常一樣來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜此所賜 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:19.81,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,560)}螺旋迷宮中沉睡的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉頰上沾到奶油了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…我沒忘記這個 也一起帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 妳還是一如既往的一副很了不起的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東洋少年出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是為了帶走幼狼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨 不用管他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且目標獵物自行落網了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到魔術幻燈秀 布萊恩·羅斯可殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有邀請函就這樣冒昧來訪 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 能有像您這麼有名的人大駕光臨此地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真是光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在此次宴會中披露的 並不是魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是貨真價實的奇蹟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也這麼聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我作為將來的參考 請務必讓我見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我就盡情開心一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬆懈對他的監視
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定和柯蒂麗亞·蓋洛共同行動才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅傑這老鼠…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個機器是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻燈機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是投射影像的機械
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有照片圖畫的話 就能自由地投影圖像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意在這裡就說明…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 自己一個人在那邊恍然大悟的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？跑來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿身褶邊的纖細小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬆開你那下流的手 你這個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是漢特先生 是賣鐘錶的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他在火車上認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提 那是機油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在指甲縫裡有稍微弄髒了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是裝了磷粉的氣球啊 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不工作了？賣鐘錶的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前歸程火車也沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟妳在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得能大大地開拓眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背景裡有隱藏著什麼可以支撐身體的道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 彈簧裝置嗎 吊在滑車上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍裡裝的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錫和水混合後的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一擠壓就會碎成粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個射向客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後咬住事先準備好的真子彈給大家看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低劣的機關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你們兩個都好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在裝什麼不懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔術是你最擅長的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是你啊 老大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 見到你女兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見到女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把她藏哪去了 死神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你連我女兒也想帶走的話 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你這傢伙將會背負上更深重的罪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同伴在等我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 大家注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是姐姐卡蜜拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妹妹摩瑞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們是自古以來就這村子附近大名鼎鼎的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有魔力的家族的最後倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是最後的古老力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是費爾姐妹的姐妹衣櫥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位睜大眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細觀賞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置交換了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經這片大陸上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:09:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿了古老力量的歐洲到處洋溢著魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將其視為理所當然的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒煤炭的火車奔馳著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中飛著飛船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠著電波就能將遠處人們的聲音傳到耳邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些的確是好發展
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但另一方面我們是不是忘記了什麼重要的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 比如在那邊的這位先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們重要的力量是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是科學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算剛剛親眼見證了奇蹟卻還是如此認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裡算奇蹟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣認為的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也進這個箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進這個箱子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對無法用科學說明的古老力量的偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代的傲慢年輕人喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會對你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落下審判的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓我來證明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都只是機關而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就可以成為手腕上的繩子沒被解開的證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有落地的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止他 不然的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古老的魔力喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再次讓我們見識一下奇蹟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩瑞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才那把佩劍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但手還是被綁在一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快離開帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 別把這煙霧吸進去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這煙裡充滿了幻覺劑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是為了讓觀眾覺得在夜會上表演的魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這霧也太濃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這裡等著 我馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去 久城…裡面…裡面很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩 為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是想對維多利加做些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又見面了啊 久城一彌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂麗亞小姐 您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺物箱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學院也挺能幹的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們慢了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁斷之箱已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 把這個交給那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉告她要解開謎題 為了生存而展現力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 請和維多利加見一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一直很想見妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至都在我面前哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經停下散霧器了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有被人動過手腳的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和幼狼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 再陪我一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想吸引他們的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個欺詐師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概10年前你也在這裡矇騙了德國軍隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致人落下的瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩 是你當時在這別西卜的頭骨做得好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 使用那個幻燈機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道當時你為什麼會幫助科學院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個我更想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年後的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你和母親會特意來此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:15:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和靈異部都在尋找著某樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狼喲 妳有想過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後將會是以新大陸為代表的科學時代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種世界中得到力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是我們這種古老種族 也不是靈異部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了增強他們勢力所需的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是遺物箱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大戰時我藏在那個幻燈機房間裡的禁斷的秘密之箱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像有點說漏嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 沒用的幼狼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩 到底在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中世紀的遙遠過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說當時懼怕黑死病蔓延而躲在這裡的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑色的死之使者帶去了冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東洋的黑色死神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚來到此地又是為了帶走誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為搭乘那輛火車的會是我妻子柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她沒出現 取而代之出現的卻是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還算是個不錯的餘興節目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我搭話時你的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想像得還要慌亂啊 久城一彌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是維多利加的父親 亞伯特·德·布洛瓦侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神啊 你帶來了許多事件與死亡 幹得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託你的福 我的幼狼得以磨練頭腦 離完成又近了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了我而出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對整個歐洲來說 她也算是唯一有用的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的調整就交給我 你請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侯爵大人 水閘被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有用的道具？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為了這個才將維多利加…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要如何不全取決於我的斟酌決定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保全國家大局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:18:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算如此 你也有熱愛保護維多利加的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血濃於水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還太年輕了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侯爵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要帶走維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會把她留在你這種人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那座學園也和此地一樣 都掌握在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且無論身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下一次暴風雨到來之時 無人能夠逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 動作快點 海水從水閘那邊湧進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火車在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳吸進剛才那些煙了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 來 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Masquerade號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 這下得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我自己走吧 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊 我不可能做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是來接妳的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己出生的意義都不明白 又怎麼可能奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 這樣連你都會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我見到妳父親了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人們都只會自說自話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們也有在認真煩惱 思考 並生存著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存的意義之後再慢慢考慮就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為此而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你找到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜此所賜我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做回了…一個溫和的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定要保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 抓住這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別西卜的頭骨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被「死亡」詛咒的要塞 蠅王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠你啊 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個難道是媽媽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還托我傳話給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開謎題 為了生存而展現力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且她還說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親仍然愛著嬌小的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使妳不哭泣 我也會像這樣趕去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生存而展現的力量…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.29,0:24:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 加油啊 fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你就不能閉嘴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:19.91,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,560)}漆黑列車承載著數個謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:40.38,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:49.72,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新たな旅立ち 迎えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:59.76,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失いかけていた　Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.76,0:23:04.74,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼び覚ましたconfined　in you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:14.43,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共にした日々を強く握り緊め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:19.60,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:23.79,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互いに寄り添い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:28.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れる事などない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:34.12,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇が二人分かつとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:39.40,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かな鼓動が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:43.45,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう告げているから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:48.23,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再び出会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:24:00.60,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想いよ　どうか君と共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:40.38,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:49.72,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接新的启程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:59.76,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追逐着失落之物　Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.76,0:23:04.74,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒被囚禁中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:14.43,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力握紧朝夕共处的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:19.60,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:23.79,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要互相靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:28.70,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无害怕之事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:34.12,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使黑暗终将分开你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:39.40,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明确的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:43.45,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:48.23,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到与你再次相遇那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:24:00.60,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望这份思念能伴你左右

